29
00:01:25,936 --> 00:01:26,937
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo?</font>

30
00:01:27,504 --> 00:01:29,206
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ibunya Yeon Ju.</font>

31
00:01:29,606 --> 00:01:31,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Segera datang ke rumahku!</font>

32
