1056
01:05:12,792 --> 01:05:14,060
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Putri ketua ada di sini.</i></font>

1057
01:05:14,060 --> 01:05:15,128
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia benar-benar berwajah dua.</i></font>

1058
01:05:15,128 --> 01:05:17,397
